author: spoorend
title: Eeyore's birthday surprise
review: Nice set with some really unique parts. Must have for Pooh fans. This set contains the unique Winnie the Pooh and Eeyore donkey character. Also the cake and present box are nice parts. The yellow table can be used in combination with other stories and the Winnie the Pooh sign can also be used as a railway station sign.

author: jinxjinx550
title: They forgot Eeyore's present!
review:
I do love this set.  The figures are great and the cake is a dream come true.  But I was very disappointed that they didn't include the useful pot to put things in that Pooh actually brought Eeyore in the Winnie the Pooh books.  

Colors are also very nice, but you truly need other Winnie the Pooh sets to build up a realistic world to play with these pieces in.
